{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_08_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 御利益がないかなって",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "社務所でいただいたパンフレットによれば\nこの周辺には、他にも三つ神社があるそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "According to the pamphlet we got from the shrine office‚\nthere are three more shrines around here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "結構多いな\nとなると、どういう順番で回るかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a lot.\nThen‚ in what order should we visit them…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6336.666666700001,
          "startTime": 15.97
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "少しだけ待って下さい\n最短で回れるルートを、今考えますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please wait a moment.\nI’m thinking of the fastest route right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6790.000000000001,
          "startTime": 22.39
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7170,
          "startTime": 22.77
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ここはバスに乗って……\nその次は、電車で行ってから歩いた方が早いわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll take the bus from here…\nand for the next one‚ it’ll be faster to take the train and then walk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました。……この神社を出た所に\nバス停があるので、まずそれに乗りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting. …There’s a bus stop\nright outside this shrine‚ so let’s take that first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "速いな、もう調べ終わったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was fast. Have you already finished checking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "地図を眺めるのは、割と好きなんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I quite enjoy looking at maps.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "どういう順番で回れば一番効率がいいかって考えるのは\nパズルみたいで楽しくありませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about the most efficient order to visit places\nis like a puzzle‚ don’t you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、千紗もあまり分かってはくれないんですけど……\n私のスタンプラリーには付き合ってくれるんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Chisa doesn’t really understand it…\nbut she does come along with me on my stamp rallies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺も、そういう難しいのはあんまり……\nでも、沙季らしいなと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not really good with complicated things like that either…\nbut I think it’s very like you‚ Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。それに今回だって\n御朱印を効率よく集めるのに役立ってるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. And this time too‚\nit’s helpful for efficiently collecting goshuin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nそういう言い方はいけません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nyou shouldn't talk about it like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1787021092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "御朱印は、神様とのご縁が出来た証ですから\nただ集めて、数を自慢するだけのものではないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Goshuin is proof of a connection with the gods‚ so\nit’s not something you just collect and boast about the number of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "功徳の証でもあるので、亡くなった後に\n御朱印帳を棺に入れてあげるのもいいそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s also proof of merit‚ so when someone passes away‚\nit’s good to put the goshuincho in the coffin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどなぁー……\nさすが、御朱印のことも予習してたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nAs expected‚ you did your research on goshuin too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "はい。……ロケ中は緊張して\n話す前に噛んでしまったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. …But I was so nervous during the filming\nthat I stumbled over my words before I could even speak.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、この神社を出た所にバス停がありますから\nまずはそれに乗って、次の神社に向かいましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ there’s a bus stop right outside this shrine‚\nso let’s take that and head to the next shrine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "これで、二ヶ所目の神社にもお参り完了……と\n年末なせいか、神社の人達も忙しそうでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ we’ve finished visiting the second shrine…\nIt seems the shrine staff are busy because it’s the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "正月の神社は、忙しい所の騒ぎじゃないだろうけどなぁ\nそれにしても、うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t imagine how busy they must be at the shrine during the New Year…\nBy the way‚ hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.350363357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.8999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ、バスがなかなか来ませんね\n時刻表には、十五分前とあるんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ the bus isn’t coming.\nIt was supposed to arrive 15 minutes ago‚ according to the timetable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "年末で渋滞にでもはまってるのかな\nしかし移動にあまり時間が掛かると……うーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it’s stuck in traffic because it's the end of the year.\nBut if it takes too long to get there… hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ、ラジオのスタジオに移動を始めないと\n収録に間に合わなくなりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to start heading to the radio studio soon‚\nor we'll be late for the recording.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。悪いが、神社巡りはまた今度にしよう\n次の休みに、また俺も付き合うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Sorry‚ but let’s do the shrine visits another time.\nI’ll go with you again on my next day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.4999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "……はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（でも神社巡りをしたいと言った時の沙季は）\n（めずらしいくらい、食い下がってたよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But when Saki said she wanted to go to the shrines‚）\n（she was unusually insistent.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.0333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なあ、沙季\nなんで、そんな焦って神社に行きたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Saki.\nWhy do you want to visit the shrines in such a hurry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "それは、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.666666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.8999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、やましいことではないんです\nただ……今の私が言うには、ちょっと問題があるので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that I have anything to hide.\nIt’s just… it’s a bit problematic for me to say it now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.1013761889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.666666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "私達……月ストとサニピは\nNEXT VENUSグランプリで優勝しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We… Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace…\nwon the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、それは凄く嬉しかったです\nさっきのロケでも、皆さんに声を掛けてもらいましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I was very happy about that.\nEven during the shoot earlier‚ people were calling out to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.633324178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.7666570027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "でも何日か経ったら、じわじわ恐くなってきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But after a few days‚ I started to get scared…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.7666570027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……恐い？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Scared?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.2333236694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "これから私達に向けられる目は、変わると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think the way people look at us is going to change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.7999903361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.0666570027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "無名の新人から、リズノワやトリエルみたいな\n強豪を倒して優勝した、期待のアイドルに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From unknown rookies to promising idols\nwho defeated strong contenders like LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE and won.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.4283917136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "その肩書きと期待に見合うだけのパフォーマンスを\nこれからの私達は出来るんだろうか……と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was wondering if we'd be able to deliver performances\nthat live up to that title and those expectations… from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.5666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.0666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（これからが正念場だと沙季は分かってる）\n（だからこそ、無責任に「大丈夫だ」とは言えないよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saki understands that this is a crucial time.）\n（So‚ I can’t just irresponsibly tell her “it’ll be okay”.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.4666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.0999974568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "神頼みをしても、結局、これまで以上に\n努力するしかないことは分かっています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that even if I pray to the gods‚\nin the end‚ all we can do is work harder than ever before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.1999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "でも、皆の分まで神社を回って御朱印を集めたら\nちょっとぐらい御利益がないかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I thought that if I went around to all the shrines and collected goshuin for everyone‚\nmaybe there would be some kind of divine favor…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.7999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 240.4666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（努力を積み重ねるしかないっていうのは正しい）\n（けど、不安を減らせるなら神頼みにも意味はあるよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s true that all we can do is keep working hard‚）\n（but if it can ease her anxiety‚ then there’s meaning in praying.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.9621980358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "沙季は、このままラジオの収録に向かってくれ\nゲストがいないんじゃ、番組が成り立たないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki‚ head to the radio recording.\nIf there’s no guest‚ the program won’t be able to proceed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.2999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
